data.description: Welcome to 529 Crutcher CT! This 4 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath home offers unparalleled upgrades and high-end finishes. An open floor plan welcomes you with a large kitchen island and a gas cooktop. The spacious utility room is perfect for laundry, storage and the office provides an extra workspace. Upstairs you'll find a bonus room for added entertainment space and relaxation. The backyard is immaculate with a fenced in yard for privacy and protection. Enjoy the spacious bedrooms each with plenty of room to relax. Huge walk-in closets. This is such a wonderful neighborhood! Here you will find many amenities and events to enjoy. There is a community garden to explore and enjoy. A pond for fishing and relaxing as well as hiking trails. There are regular movie nights to enjoy. Plus, there is a special dog park and a playground for the children. And, of course, a beautiful pool to stay cool in. Come enjoy all the extras and see this beautiful home for yourself, you won't be disappointed!
